1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:39,169 --> 00:01:41,120
[Shooting Stars]
[EP02]

3
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:58,560
[Flowers for sale!]

4
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:00,960
Sir, sir!

5
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,720
Would you like to buy some flowers?

6
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:09,000
What's happening inside?

7
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:10,600
Not sure.

8
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:11,560
They're making arrests.

9
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,720
Have they caught anyone?

10
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,400
Not a clue.

11
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,080
Can I leave it here with you for now?

12
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:20,200
I'll come back for it shortly.

13
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,760
Sure, no problem.

14
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:25,400
Thanks.

15
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:28,160
I'm telling you,

16
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:28,720
these days

17
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:29,520
they just arrest people left and right.

18
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,200
What's going on up there?

19
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,440
Captain Chen, how was your day?

20
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,440
Hi, Captain Chen.

21
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,800
Captain Chen, you're back.

22
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,160
I slid your letter under your door.

23
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:46,800
What did you say?

24
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,680
I put your letter inside your room.

25
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,360
Young man, slow down when you run.

26
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,320
[Don't trip and fall.]

27
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,400
[Take care as autumn turns chilly,]

28
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,200
[stick to your path]

29
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,000
[and do not worry about us.]

30
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:20,840
[May all your bridges be sturdy]

31
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,840
[and all your tunnels bright.]

32
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,240
[Captain.]

33
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,200
Captain,

34
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,760
they're from the household registration.

35
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,680
These are all invalidated,

36
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:01,440
yet to be canceled

37
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,560
at the Public Security Bureau.

38
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,800
These are empty households.

39
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,280
The owners have moved out of the area.

40
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,640
I'd like to borrow

41
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:20,080
this card for a week.

42
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,080
Then I will destroy it.

43
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,800
No matter what happens,

44
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,640
no one will use

45
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:27,120
this card again.

46
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:29,000
After a week,

47
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,480
you just need to go through the normal procedure

48
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,200
at the registration office to cancel it,

49
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,400
nothing else.

50
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:34,800
Understood.

51
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,360
Are you trying to ask me

52
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:44,200
when I'll end your dormant state?

53
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,240
When?

54
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,360
We need to wait a bit longer.

55
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,360
The central committee has sent

56
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,000
someone to Shanghai

57
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,240
for organization rebuilding.

58
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:57,760
But our force was

59
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,560
greatly weakened in the KMT controlled area.

60
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:03,960
Now, the most important thing

61
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,680
is to preserve our strength.

62
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,360
If it weren't for this

63
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,400
particular situation,

64
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,240
I shouldn't have asked you

65
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,200
to help me with the documentation.

66
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:15,440
I understand.

67
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,320
I'll wait patiently.

68
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:17,680
Can't find anywhere

69
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,520
to stay?

70
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:23,640
I don't know who to turn to.

71
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,000
Don't you have any relatives in Shanghai?

72
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,880
What about your parents' friends?

73
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,760
I don't know them.

74
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:38,520
In fact, I had a French teacher.

75
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,320
However,

76
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,520
she left Shanghai

77
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:44,320
a few days ago

78
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,360
and I don't know

79
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,000
when she will return.

80
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,600
I can't go back

81
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,880
to my own home now,

82
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:55,400
can I?

83
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,760
The bedroom is yours. I'll take the couch.

84
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:28,800
Sir,

85
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,160
did you come to Shanghai

86
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,400
from somewhere else?

87
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:34,200
I've already bought a train ticket

88
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,240
back to Nanjing in three days.

89
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,040
Until then,

90
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:37,200
you can stay here.

91
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:39,240
I'll also

92
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,640
cover your meals.

93
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,320
Other than that,

94
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,960
I'm not responsible for anything.

95
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,560
Deal?

96
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:46,440
Deal.

97
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,320
What grade are you in?

98
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:52,400
Second grade. I'm 8 years old.

99
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,440
If anyone asks,

100
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:55,840
we'll say

101
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,880
we're cousins.

102
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,760
Okay.

103
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,640
Any more questions?

104
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:03,320
What's your name?

105
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:12,880
I'm Hua Zhen.

106
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,120
What's the matter?

107
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:28,880
Brother Hua Zhen,

108
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:30,120
how much do you

109
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,320
earn a month?

110
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:32,520
What?

111
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,560
Is it a lot?

112
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:38,200
40 silver dollars every month.

113
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:39,680
I'm not sure if that's a lot.

114
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,360
[Hua Zhen,]

115
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,000
[I need a favor.]

116
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,680
[Does it matter a lot to you?]

117
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:30,680
Extremely.

118
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,200
[It must remain a secret]

119
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,080
[from anyone else.]

120
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:52,200
Liang, this is Zhen speaking.

121
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,080
I need your help

122
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,080
with something.

123
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:18,880
I'm stepping out.

124
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,960
You should keep a low profile.

125
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:23,680
But I have

126
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:25,240
an important call to make.

127
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,560
I know you're looking

128
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,600
for a place to stay,

129
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,880
but it's best to keep out of sight

130
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:32,960
until the culprit is caught.

131
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,800
How about you come with me?

132
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,320
I've said before,

133
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,480
I only provide you with food and shelter,

134
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,000
not

135
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,080
anything else.

136
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:11,600
Excuse me,

137
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,160
may I use the phone,

138
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:13,840
please?

139
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,320
Why

140
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:17,240
are you alone?

141
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,480
Where are your parents?

142
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,840
Why aren't they with you?

143
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:21,480
They're in the room.

144
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,360
If

145
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,440
something happens to

146
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,360
a child like you

147
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,200
in our hotel,

148
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,560
we would be blamed.

149
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:29,840
Could you

150
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,320
write down your room number here?

151
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,200
In case of anything special,

152
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,360
I can contact your parents,

153
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:33,960
okay?

154
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,040
Just write it here.

155
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:48,920
Thanks, but...

156
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:51,280
my parents are upstairs,

157
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:53,440
I just need the phone

158
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,560
and I won't wander off.

159
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:57,400
Alright then.

160
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:58,880
Thank you.

161
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:10,040
Duoci, this is all I have.

162
00:14:10,040 --> 00:14:11,360
It's yours now.

163
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,760
Thank you, Yimo.

164
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:14,040
It's just...

165
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,520
could I possibly borrow

166
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:17,040
some money from you?

167
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:17,920
Not much.

168
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,400
Here, Duoci.

169
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:22,760
I'll pay you back for this.

170
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:24,160
Where are your mom and dad?

171
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,680
Um...

172
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:29,040
is Luoyan home?

173
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:30,800
Bye.

174
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:31,920
Bye.

175
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,160
See you.

176
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:42,680
Is this Yubai speaking?

177
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:49,040
Oh, okay, thank you.

178
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:52,400
I only have 6.2 Silver dollars,

179
00:14:52,400 --> 00:14:53,560
here you are.

180
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:57,040
Thank you.

181
00:14:57,040 --> 00:14:58,080
You're welcome.

182
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:00,440
Take care.

183
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:01,400
Bye.

184
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:51,000
Staying in your room all day?

185
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:53,920
There's nowhere to go.

186
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:32,080
Hello?

187
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:32,920
Brother,

188
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:34,680
how's the investigation

189
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:35,400
I asked you about?

190
00:16:36,920 --> 00:16:37,880
I was about to tell you about that

191
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:39,280
even if you didn't call.

192
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:41,440
[Deng Mingyuan is in big trouble.]

193
00:16:41,880 --> 00:16:42,840
[From now on,]

194
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:43,960
[you must distance yourself from him,]

195
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,760
[or you'll end up in trouble too.]

196
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:47,280
What kind of trouble?

197
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:51,280
He's been found out as a communist.

198
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:56,800
[The day he came to Dad's birthday party,]

199
00:16:57,160 --> 00:16:58,440
he was taken away right after leaving.

200
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:00,400
The Party Affairs Investigation Bureau

201
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:02,040
has already visited Dad.

202
00:17:02,560 --> 00:17:04,040
Everyone in our family

203
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:05,280
will be investigated.

204
00:17:06,040 --> 00:17:07,000
Who took him away?

205
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:08,640
[Does that matter?]

206
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:10,160
I know you used to

207
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:10,920
say Deng Mingyuan

208
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,640
was your mentor,

209
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:14,080
[but you should stop]

210
00:17:14,080 --> 00:17:15,680
[saying that now, Okay?]

211
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:17,560
He couldn't possibly be a communist.

212
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:20,040
He accompanied the former premier to the north,

213
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:21,400
and followed the Chairman on the Northern Expedition.

214
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:23,280
He has convictions and qualifications.

215
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:24,520
How could he

216
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:25,680
join the Communist Party?

217
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:27,920
Exactly, that's why it's foolish.

218
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:30,560
He threw away a promising future

219
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,080
to join

220
00:17:32,080 --> 00:17:32,960
the Communist Party.

221
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:33,720
Brother,

222
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:37,160
if he is a communist,

223
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:40,000
what will they do to him?

224
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:42,160
[If he really is a communist,]

225
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:43,320
[he and everyone close to him]

226
00:17:43,320 --> 00:17:44,320
[could be executed.]

227
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:47,560
By the way, I must ask you,

228
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,240
did you go to Shanghai

229
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,280
at your will

230
00:17:50,280 --> 00:17:50,960
or did Deng Mingyuan

231
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:52,160
send you there for something?

232
00:17:52,560 --> 00:17:53,760
[Why did you rush off to Shanghai]

233
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:55,000
[right after meeting him?]

234
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:58,320
I was just bored at home

235
00:17:58,320 --> 00:17:59,280
and wanted to go out.

236
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:00,320
Oh,

237
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:01,840
I met a kid

238
00:18:01,840 --> 00:18:02,800
in Shanghai.

239
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:05,160
Her family has undergone some changes.

240
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:07,520
[If I bring her back to Nanjing]

241
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:09,400
[when I report to the fleet,]

242
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:10,760
[could you guys help look after her?]

243
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:14,680
What kid could you possibly know?

244
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:16,720
Did Deng Mingyuan

245
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,800
ask you to find her?

246
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:19,920
[Hua Zhen,]

247
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:21,800
[I'm officially warning you now,]

248
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:24,160
Deng Mingyuan has accomplices in Shanghai too.

249
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,680
You must distance yourself not just from him,

250
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:28,120
but also from his associates

251
00:18:28,120 --> 00:18:29,040
and their affairs!

252
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,160
[If you dare bring back someone]

253
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,120
[related to Deng Mingyuan,]

254
00:18:32,120 --> 00:18:33,880
[our whole family could be involved!]

255
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:40,960
It's just a kid

256
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:41,680
I happened to meet.

257
00:18:42,280 --> 00:18:43,200
I was just asking.

258
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:46,680
Brother,

259
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,640
if he is a communist,

260
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,000
he must know he couldn't escape

261
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,040
when he stepped into the Hua's house.

262
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:55,720
Why would he still come?

263
00:18:57,480 --> 00:19:00,160
Who knows what these communists are thinking?

264
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:02,080
Aren't you due to report back

265
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:03,640
to the fleet in a month?

266
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:06,760
You want to watch movies, visit fairs,

267
00:19:06,760 --> 00:19:08,320
eat eight-treasure duck, sweet and sour fish,

268
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:09,200
go ahead.

269
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:11,000
[Immediately return to Nanjing once you've had enough fun,]

270
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:13,120
[and stop snooping around at night,]

271
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:13,920
[got it?]

272
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:17,360
Understood.

273
00:19:47,080 --> 00:19:48,680
[Deng Mingyuan is in big trouble.]

274
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:51,560
[He's been found out as a communist.]

275
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:53,240
[From now on,]

276
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,360
[you must distance yourself from him,]

277
00:19:54,360 --> 00:19:55,880
[or you'll end up in trouble too.]

278
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:59,320
Through a thousand books, one walks with the ancients.

279
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:03,400
[You must distance yourself not just from him,]

280
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,920
[but also from his associates]

281
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,200
[and their affairs!]

282
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:07,720
[If you dare bring back someone]

283
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:08,320
[related to Deng Mingyuan,]

284
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,960
[our whole family could be involved!]

285
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,160
[Sir, here's your receipt.]

286
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:28,400
Thank you.

287
00:20:37,080 --> 00:20:38,400
I've handled the paperwork

288
00:20:38,840 --> 00:20:40,280
and reserved enough for the room.

289
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:42,320
You can

290
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:43,960
stay here

291
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:45,680
as long as you like.

292
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:46,960
You can eat

293
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:48,360
all your meals at the hotel restaurant.

