593
00:40:11,120 --> 00:40:11,640
thank you.

594
00:41:20,200 --> 00:41:21,520
The reason I came to Shanghai

595
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:23,520
was to deliver a book for someone.

596
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:25,680
It wasn't until

597
00:41:25,680 --> 00:41:27,040
I saw the ship tickets and identity papers inside the book

598
00:41:27,040 --> 00:41:27,840
that I realized

599
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,400
I wasn't just delivering a book,

600
00:41:31,760 --> 00:41:32,840
[but a chance for your family]

601
00:41:32,840 --> 00:41:33,800
[to survive.]

602
00:41:38,680 --> 00:41:41,080
Is he a very important friend to you?

603
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:45,640
More important than a friend.

604
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:47,760
To me,

605
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:49,920
he's like

606
00:41:49,920 --> 00:41:50,680
the morning star.

607
00:41:58,720 --> 00:42:00,200
Now that I've decided to stay,

608
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:02,120
there are two things you need to know.

609
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:03,880
First,

610
00:42:04,680 --> 00:42:05,800
for some reasons,

611
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,160
I can't take you back to Nanjing,

612
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:09,280
nor can I send you to an orphanage

613
00:42:09,280 --> 00:42:10,480
or foster care,

614
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:11,760
as it might

615
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:12,960
bring them trouble.

616
00:42:13,640 --> 00:42:14,680
So, for now,

617
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:16,800
you'll have to stay with me.

618
00:42:17,680 --> 00:42:18,200
Okay.

619
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:20,000
Second,

620
00:42:20,600 --> 00:42:21,200
to others, we will

621
00:42:21,200 --> 00:42:22,240
call each other cousins.

622
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:24,120
No problem.

623
00:42:29,760 --> 00:42:31,120
But I don't know how to take care of a child.

624
00:42:32,560 --> 00:42:34,080
I'm not really a child.

625
00:42:37,720 --> 00:42:38,640
Alright... Okay.

626
00:42:42,040 --> 00:42:42,760
Actually, I still

627
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:44,000
have some doubts.

628
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:45,880
Maybe catching the killer

629
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:46,800
will provide some answers.

630
00:42:47,640 --> 00:42:48,400
But after a month,

631
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:50,040
whether we catch the killer or not,

632
00:42:51,640 --> 00:42:53,280
I must return to Nanjing.

633
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:39,000
Here's your new identification.

634
00:43:39,640 --> 00:43:40,520
For now,

635
00:43:41,080 --> 00:43:42,600
your name is Li Qiushi.

636
00:43:46,240 --> 00:43:47,040
And you?

637
00:44:11,080 --> 00:44:13,080
[Xiang Yuansheng.]

638
00:44:17,000 --> 00:44:18,240
Brother Zhen,

639
00:44:19,120 --> 00:44:20,720
where are you going

640
00:44:20,720 --> 00:44:21,360
with this identity?
